<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,308,1130,1154]" pageId="9" pageNumber="44">Remarks</emphasis>
. 
<taxonomicName box="[326,596,1129,1153]" class="Insecta" family="Hybotidae" genus="Platypalpus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="44" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="layiaphilus" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[326,596,1129,1153]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="44">Platypalpus layiaphilus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[607,701,1130,1154]" pageId="9" pageNumber="44" rank="species">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[607,701,1130,1154]" pageId="9" pageNumber="44">sp. nov.</emphasis>
</taxonomicNameLabel>
is most similar to 
<taxonomicName box="[930,1073,1130,1153]" class="Insecta" family="Hybotidae" genus="Platypalpus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="44" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cummingi" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[930,944,1130,1153]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="44">P</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[963,1073,1130,1153]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="44">cummingi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1084,1179,1130,1154]" pageId="9" pageNumber="44" rank="species">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1084,1179,1130,1154]" pageId="9" pageNumber="44">sp. nov.</emphasis>
</taxonomicNameLabel>
The main differences between these species are given below in the key.
</paragraph>
